```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Auditor
    participant Caten8

    Auditor ->> Caten8: Log in to the Caten8 system
    Caten8 -->> Auditor: Authenticate user credentials
    Auditor ->> Caten8: Access relevant documentation and records
    Caten8 ->> Auditor: Provide access to the requested documents
    Auditor ->> Caten8: Review change control records
    Caten8 -->> Auditor: Provide change control records
    Auditor ->> Caten8: Analyze risk assessment records
    Caten8 -->> Auditor: Provide risk assessment records
    Auditor ->> Caten8: Evaluate compliance with policies and regulations
    Caten8 -->> Auditor: Provide compliance documentation and records
    Auditor ->> Caten8: Generate audit findings and recommendations
    Caten8 -->> Auditor: Store audit findings and recommendations
    Auditor ->> Caten8: Complete the assessment process
    Caten8 -->> Auditor: Confirm completion of the assessment

```
